                        "Exception during stop by stop timer");
                }
            }

            if (debug) {
                //Logging.report(Logging.INFORMATION, LogChannels.LC_MMAPI,
                System.out.println("+++ stop by stop time control (STOPPED_AT_TIME) +++");
